aws_api_gateway_api_key.description: Provides an API Gateway API Key.

name.description: The name of the API key

description.description: The API key description. Defaults to "Managed by Terraform".

enabled.description: Specifies whether the API key can be used by callers. Defaults to `true`.

value.description: The value of the API key. If not specified, it will be automatically generated by AWS on creation.

id.description: The ID of the API key

created_date.description: The creation date of the API key

last_updated_date.description: The last update date of the API key

value.description: The value of the API key
